primaryTopic.definition: The School of Physical, Environmental and Mathematical Sciences encompasses the disciplines of Chemistry, Geography, Mathematics, Statistics, Oceanography and Physics. The School of PEMS is one of four Schools at UNSW Canberra, the academic component of the Australian Defence Force Academy located in Canberra.
